Notes:
	•	This version does not subtract a day—it uses the exact day you put in the summary message.
	•	Because PK = yyyyMMdd#agentId, the query is single-partition and efficient.
	•	If you prefer to fetch only one event’s count, change the filter to:

PartitionKey eq '<day#agentId>' and RowKey ge '<eventKey>#' and RowKey lt '<eventKey>~'

and count the rows.

